timing_disabl...to_data_checks(25.10)    timing_disabl...to_data_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_user_data_to_data_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_user_data_to_data_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set to true, disables data to data checks that are created by the
       set_data_check command. This global variable does  not  affect  non-se-
       quential timing checks described in the timing library.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

